creator: AZEM
descriptionHtml:
-imagine an app which understand you, help you make money, buy your favorite game's currency and buy gift cards.
-with easy and simple ways to sign up and log in.
-isn't it awesome, you also will try your luck with lucky tow and win special gifts.
the ways to earn crowns are simple and easy as watch a video or do a simple survey or task.
-easy and several ways to contact with us, sending your complain or your feedback.
-there are daily offers that will make it easy for you to buy whatever you need.
-you will be rewarded if you invite you friends to our community.
-soon... the crown store and lucky spinner will be available
descriptionShort: imagine an app which understand you and help you make money.
